Fihirana . Mihirà fihiram @-@ baovao ho an' i Jehovah ; Fa efa nanao fahagagana Izy ; Ny tanany ankavanana sy ny sandriny masina no nahavitany famonjena . ||| Sing to the Lord a new song , for he performs amazing deeds ! His right hand and his mighty arm accomplish deliverance .
Jehovah efa nampahafantatra ny famonjeny ; Teo imason' ny jentilisa no nanehoany ny fahamarinany . ||| The Lord demonstrates his power to deliver ; in the sight of the nations he reveals his justice .
Efa nahatsiaro ny famindram @-@ pony sy ny fahamarinany tamin' ny taranak' i Isiraely Izy ; Efa nahita ny famonjen' Andriamanitsika ny vazan @-@ tany rehetra . ||| He remains loyal and faithful to the family of Israel . All the ends of the earth see our God deliver us .
Mihobia ho an' i Jehovah , ry tany rehetra , Velomy ny hoby , ka mihirà . ||| Shout out praises to the Lord , all the earth ! Break out in a joyful shout and sing !
Mankalazà an' i Jehovah amin' ny lokanga , Dia amin' ny lokanga sy ny feo fihirana , ||| Sing to the Lord accompanied by a harp , accompanied by a harp and the sound of music !
Amin' ny trompetra sy ny fitsofana ny anjomara , Ka mihobia eo anatrehan' i Jehovah Mpanjaka . ||| With trumpets and the blaring of the ram 's horn , shout out praises before the king , the Lord !
Aoka hirohondrohona ny ranomasina sy izay rehetra ao aminy , Izao rehetra izao sy ny mponina eo aminy . ||| Let the sea and everything in it shout , along with the world and those who live in it !
Aoka hiteha @-@ tanana ny riaka ; Aoka hiara @-@ mihoby aminy koa ny tendrombohitra ||| Let the rivers clap their hands ! Let the mountains sing in unison
Eo anatrehan' i Jehovah , fa avy hitsara ny tany Izy ; Hitsara izao rehetra izao amin' ny fahamarinana Izy Ary ny firenena amin' ny fahitsiana . ||| before the Lord ! For he comes to judge the earth ! He judges the world fairly , and the nations in a just manner .
